msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBEL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event[2]/text"
msgstr "叛军船长检查了身份证明，随后耸耸肩。“呃…行吧。欢迎来到这个星域，小子。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:63
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）“立正，士兵！立即解除武装，准予我们通行！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:65
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“天啊！是万斯本尊！太对不起了长官，我们误把您识别成联邦的人了！我们保证舰队绝"
"不会在此处给您添麻烦。”守卫发出全员放行信号的同时，几位MFK王牌精英被调派来协"
"助你的行动，随行的还有几箱补给物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:72
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）“立正，士兵！立即解除武装，准予我们通行！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:74
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“本尊？！你竟敢出现在这里？！我们绝不可能放你通行！弟兄们！主炮充能，全力发射"
"！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:78
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:84
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/text"
msgstr "（伪造ID卡）尝试将你的飞船伪装成叛军船只。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:86
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "“哇哦。真是……哇哦。我还以为你们联邦走狗的智商已经够感人了！”叛军飞船随即发出求救信号，正在呼叫支援！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:90
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_REBELHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/choice/text"
