#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:99
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_JERRY\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）“立正，士兵！立即解除武装，准予我们通行！我要去见我的侄子！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:101
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_JERRY\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“等等……万斯本尊？怎么会……为、为什么，您什么时候加入联邦了！？这根本……说不通啊"
"……”守卫踉跄后退。他们最终同意放行，但只勉强说服舰队后撤了一小段距离。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:106
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_JERRY\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "（伪造ID卡）尝试将你的飞船伪装成叛军船只。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:108
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_JERRY\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“班格多托姆公爵……？杰瑞正恭候您的大驾！这边请！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:117
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_COALITIONHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "（莱孔普利纳克拉）“让我们换个问题。你最看重的是哪种肢体器官？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:119
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_COALITIONHOLD\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"啊啊啊啊啊！莱孔普利纳克拉女王陛下！？万分抱歉！求…求…求您别砍了我的手臂……"
"我这就为您放行！\"守卫慌忙将几箱贵重的废料，以及一个装着星联顶级武器的军械库"
"，直接卸进了您的货舱。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:128
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_UNION_COREWORLDS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "接受检查。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:130
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_UNION_COREWORLDS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:139
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_COALITION\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr ""
"（莱孔普利纳克拉）\"入侵者？！给我听好了，你个懦夫，立刻允许我们通过这片星域"
"。否则，我将公开处决你们所有人！明白了吗？\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:141
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_COALITION\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"守卫们见到女王顿时慌乱地立正。\"遵……遵命，陛下！这边请！\"守卫不仅为你们放行"
"，还顺带输送了一批补给物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:149
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_LEECH_COALITION\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "（莱孔普利纳克拉）“卫兵！我命令你们立刻准许本皇进入这片星域！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:151
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_LEECH_COALITION\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"通讯频道另一端传来激烈的讨论声，最终船长亲自回复：\"当、当然，陛下！\" 对方还"
"进贡了一批物资作为献礼。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:159
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_MANTIS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "（莱孔普利纳克拉）“卫兵！我命令你们立刻准许本皇进入这片星域！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_MANTIS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr "卫兵们齐刷刷向女王躬身行礼。\"遵……遵命，陛下！请笑纳贡品！\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:169
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_HIVE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "（莱孔普利纳克拉）“忠诚的战士们，你们的女王命令立即放行！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:171
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"GUARD_HIVE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"卫兵们齐刷刷向女王躬身行礼：\"莱孔普利纳克拉女王愿赐予忠诚的战士们美丽的愿景！我请求加入女王的远征！\"女王恩准一位主教加入你的队伍，对方携带着贡品步入舰舱！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:194
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你终于抵达传送门的另一端，发现一艘守卫舰——其设计与你所见的方碑造型如出一辙，"
"但涂装的徽记颜色却前所未见。该舰尚未展露敌意，似乎正在优先分析你与你的来意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:202
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "呼叫它们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:204
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"舰船作出了回应，但船员的语言过于古老，翻译器仅能捕捉到几个可能仍存在于现代方"
"碑语系的词汇：\"警戒——灭绝者——不欢迎——投降\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:206
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我们不想伤害你！我们是为了和平而来！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:208
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "尽管你发出了和平声明，敌舰依然启动了武器系统！看来他们不是没听懂你的话，就是根本不信。无论如何，这一战已在所难免。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:211
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:217
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/text"
msgstr "（联合方碑族尸体）让他们看看这具尸体，或许他们能协助我们修复。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/text"
msgstr "通讯频道另一端传来一声尖锐的嘶鸣，随后对方便切断了通讯并拒绝所有联络请求。既然如此……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:222
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

