"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_ANCIENT_NO_COMMONWEALTH\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:239
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/text"
msgstr "（联合方碑族船员）你的联合方碑族船员想和它们说话。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:241
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你那联合方碑船员的身影让他们立刻放松下来，对方马上关闭了武器系统。经过沟通，"
"你的联合方碑船员说服他们安装了一台翻译器，能把古老的联合方碑语言转换成通用语"
"。\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"刚才的敌意很抱歉，只要有外人出现我们就会高度戒备。当年被灭绝者追"
"杀的阴影到现在还挥之不去。我们是联合方碑的人，欢迎来到这个简陋的避难所。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:246
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "灭绝者？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:248
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"方碑族点了点它的立方体头：\"那些粉白身体的存在，当年下令灭绝我们的族群，其力"
"量让我们毫无招架之力。他们至今仍在某处游荡，若是找到这里……恐怕我们这最后的血"
"脉就要彻底消失了。\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t它静默片刻后继续道：\"没想到你会收容我们的同胞。早该探测到的，"
"看来我们的设备已大不如前。熵增定律真是位残酷的女神。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:253
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我们该怎么离开这个星区？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:255
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"联合方碑族摇了摇头：\"恐怕没那么简单。我的其他同胞未必欢迎外人，即便是庇护过我们的人。不过若你们执意离开，就去寻找星域深处的裂隙吧——那是唯一的出口，也有我们最强大的舰船看守。做好战斗准备，从来没有人被允许离开过。\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"即便如此，我会尽力帮助你们修复船体，并赠予一件我们的武器。愿和平与你们同在，外来者。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:261
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "谢谢你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:263
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "守卫点头致意，随后与你道别。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:267
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_BEACON_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:273
msgid ""
